{"tid":51301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱兩萬賣初夜救癌母　「女大生」實為賣淫女","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T10:51:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"711001f829f323fbb4a3d876fc7fe5bbaff47282","tid":51301,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_02b.jpg?20161222200624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161222200624&h=94c9da6e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n湖南長沙一名自稱18歲、正在讀大學醫科的女子，聲稱因母親病重，急需籌措醫藥費，以兩萬元（人民幣‧下同）賣「初夜」救母。惟警方追查後發現，所謂「母親病重」只是女子為賣淫賺錢編造的謊言，她更很可能是由賣淫集團在背後操控。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_03b.jpg?20161222200624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161222200624&h=15ecbf49&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n琪琪與吳見面時顯得不耐煩，只想和吳開房。（電視畫面） <br />\n<br />\n當地一名吳姓市民早前收到女子琪琪（化名）發來的短訊，琪琪自稱是長沙一間大學的一年級醫科生，今年18歲，因母親患乳腺癌，花光所有積蓄，急需兩萬元治病，所以提出賣「初夜」以換取母親的醫藥費。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_04b.jpg?20161222200624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20161222200624&h=24f4883e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n校方指，琪琪的學生證是偽造，並非該校學生。（電視畫面） <br />\n<br />\n吳男對於琪琪的情況心生憐憫，遂相約見面。兩人商談時，琪琪顯得不耐煩，並主動開口要和吳開房。當吳提出可以無償幫助，不需要琪琪出賣「初夜」來償還時，豈料琪琪立即變了臉，然後離開現場。 <br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒跟蹤追查，發現琪琪與吳見面後，獨自前往學校，但沒返回宿舍，亦沒去教學樓，只是在校園內就餐。不久後，琪琪更由一輛豪車接走。傳媒其後向校方詢問，校方一看琪琪提供的學生證照片，認定學生證是偽造。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/photo/bkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_05b.jpg?20161222200624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161222112722804-1222_05011_001_05b.jpg%3F20161222200624&h=a5d1ed19&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n琪琪在酒店與吳見面時被警方查獲。（電視畫面） <br />\n<br />\n琪琪周一上午再次向吳發微信求助，並相約在酒店見面。吳答應赴約，但事先報警備案。兩人一見面，琪琪堅持賣「初夜」換取現金，不過她又強調，只要出得起錢，她可以提供長期服務。警方隨後趕到現場，發現琪琪並非大學生，只是借「母親病重」為藉口賣淫。 <br />\n<br />\n法律界人士稱，琪琪的行為與非法賣淫無異，她以「家庭困難」為由賺錢更已涉嫌詐騙。警方又相信，琪琪由賣淫集團在背後操控，該集團很可能以「女大學生賣處」為由，組織女子賣淫。"},{"pid":"27edba8cb7e248afe231e53d173cc0174da816ad","tid":51301,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70324760cc1ce9080807a74c475ad4feee2f6d3d","tid":51301,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:32:36.000Z","msg":"唔洗比人屌即收兩萬反而黑面"},{"pid":"fb9b7ac75073c95c40bd7bdc29677201dce309c0","tid":51301,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"由豪華車接走？<br />\n為興趣做雞"},{"pid":"9dca3cf4e18eb5c03431f7996b90de8455ed2384","tid":51301,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由豪華車接走？<br />\n為興趣做雞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能俾第二個老闆包左"},{"pid":"5bd640f8d16efb5804971be87a2e4eb997e80eb5","tid":51301,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗比人屌即收兩萬反而黑面</blockquote><br />\n有職業道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e8a746fbe3331ac806d607c88f14d2318e170","tid":51301,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"大陸妹都值2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f747d47eedf47d1c5da996b797674d397d7700f","tid":51301,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"湖南"},{"pid":"d6bb43e1ed7e637a084ae25d71ad9f66097ae629","tid":51301,"uid":60856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"湖南點解咁多雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1d9a58dc23393c8fdc200e72024985c7c81c7a","tid":51301,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f09dd253c8b814e48d87216c5ccba0e7361131","tid":51301,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"中國女人有邊個唔係賣淫女？"}]}